<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Selamat Datang di {{companyName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #f2f4f8;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Arial, sans-serif;
            color: #1f2937;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 620px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .card {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.07);
        }
        .header {
            padding: 24px 28px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb 0%, #0891b2 100%);
            color: #ffffff;
        }
        .brand {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.2px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 28px;
        }
        .title {
            margin: 0 0 12px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #0f172a;
        }
        p {
            margin: 0 0 16px;
            font-size: 15px;
        }
        .feature-box {
            margin: 18px 0 22px;
            padding: 16px;
            border: 1px solid #bfdbfe;
            border-radius: 12px;
            background-color: #eff6ff;
        }
        .feature-box ul {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            padding-left: 18px;
        }
        .feature-box li {
            margin: 6px 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .cta-wrap {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 24px 0;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background-color: #2563eb;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer {
            padding: 0 28px 24px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #64748b;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="header">
                <p class="brand">{{companyName}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content">
                <h1 class="title">Selamat Datang</h1>

                <p>Halo {{name}},</p>
                <p>Email <strong>{{email}}</strong> sudah berhasil diverifikasi dan akun Anda telah aktif.</p>
                <p>Selamat datang di {{companyName}}. Sekarang Anda bisa mulai menjelajahi layanan dan beraktivitas dengan nyaman.</p>

                <div class="feature-box">
                    <strong>Mulai dari sini:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Jelajahi produk keramik favorit Anda.</li>
                        <li>Simpan produk ke daftar keinginan.</li>
                        <li>Pantau status pesanan secara real-time.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="cta-wrap">
                    <a href="{{frontendUrl}}" class="button">Kunjungi {{companyName}}</a>
                </div>

                <p>Butuh bantuan? Tim kami siap membantu kapan pun Anda perlukan.</p>
                <p>Salam hangat,<br>Tim {{companyName}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="footer">
                <p>© {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
                <p>Email ini dikirim otomatis, mohon tidak membalas.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>